Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.46,0:01:37.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塔的顶端?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.94,0:01:38.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.72,0:01:41.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才埃洱又看了那本古书才注意到这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.84,0:01:43.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一段是这么写的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.04,0:01:48.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,『在这通天剑塔之上有个恶魔栖息在顶端』
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.70,0:01:51.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个恶魔栖息在…顶端…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.56,0:01:52.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.40,0:01:56.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这个所谓的恶魔就是魔石索沙的主人的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.70,0:02:00.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…现在就应该站在这个剑塔的最顶端才对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.78,0:02:03.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔石索沙的…主人?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.76,0:02:04.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.80,0:02:07.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这本古书上面所写的未必全都是真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.60,0:02:08.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.42,0:02:09.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是应该上去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.26,0:02:11.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.50,0:02:13.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正我们手边也没有什么其它的线索
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.34,0:02:16.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说呢?克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.28,0:02:18.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.90,0:02:19.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.44,0:02:23.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳先到安全的地方去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.40,0:02:25.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从现在开始…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.46,0:02:27.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会有更加艰苦的战斗…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:30.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能把妳带在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.12,0:02:35.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请妳把蕾娜带到雷恩他们身边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.76,0:02:36.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.10,0:02:37.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.06,0:02:38.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.04,0:02:43.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要…留在这个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.78,0:02:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳要弄清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.26,0:02:47.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是什么勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.12,0:02:50.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也没有信心能够保证妳平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.40,0:02:51.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算这样也没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.34,0:02:54.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对不会成为你们的绊脚石
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.68,0:02:55.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就答应我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.76,0:02:57.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.52,0:03:08.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就这么决定喽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.64,0:03:10.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.30,0:03:12.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.94,0:03:47.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾修顿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.40,0:03:49.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.76,0:04:02.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳没事吧?蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.10,0:04:03.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:06.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.16,0:04:07.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.72,0:04:12.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.50,0:04:24.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪亚斯?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.90,0:04:27.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀冲击波
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.26,0:04:40.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.80,0:04:42.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用管我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:43.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.66,0:04:45.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说你还受到魔物的诅咒?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.44,0:04:47.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克劳德…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.86,0:04:48.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.40,0:04:51.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.32,0:04:52.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是吉耐的羽毛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.70,0:04:55.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,崇高的魔族之王…吉耐…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.10,0:04:58.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这根羽毛已经附加了守护的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.20,0:05:01.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把它插在那把剑上…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.56,0:05:03.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守护的力量…?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.30,0:05:06.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪亚斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.00,0:05:09.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟然…为了拿到这根羽毛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.48,0:05:11.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不顾自己生命危险去找吉耐?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.80,0:05:13.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.66,0:05:15.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.66,0:05:17.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有事等着你去做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.32,0:05:19.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你，迪亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.50,0:05:42.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:49.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.10,0:05:50.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里交给我就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.50,0:05:54.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还会再见的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.10,0:05:56.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别哭…蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.96,0:05:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪亚斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.20,0:06:02.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.00,0:06:12.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火凤破
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.02,0:06:25.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不会让你们对艾斯贝尔为所欲为的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.88,0:06:47.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.64,0:06:50.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.40,0:06:53.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有这种感觉…怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.20,0:06:55.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心中忐忑不安…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.70,0:06:59.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.22,0:07:03.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空破斩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.70,0:07:17.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克劳德，你和蕾娜先走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.70,0:07:18.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾修顿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.90,0:07:19.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:22.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里有我和艾修顿来挡住他们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.90,0:07:24.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞丽奴…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.50,0:07:26.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也得让我有个大显身手的机会嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.78,0:07:29.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那好吧  蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.90,0:07:32.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们要小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.30,0:07:38.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.40,0:07:42.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞丽奴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.58,0:07:55.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然没救了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.30,0:07:56.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎么啦?大哥?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.80,0:07:58.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古书上的解读是怎么说的啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.24,0:08:01.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后一个章节是这么写的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.66,0:08:04.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,『一切的命运最后都将交托于神圣之光』
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.18,0:08:08.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,『如果能将这道圣洁的光辉导向正轨』
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.00,0:08:11.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,『就能将恶魔毁于无形…』
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.60,0:08:14.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们完蛋了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.68,0:08:18.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥啊…我有点不太懂耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.00,0:08:19.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你念的…到底是什么意思啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.12,0:08:23.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个笨蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.16,0:08:26.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这上面所谓的光辉，当然就是拉克尔赫普了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.00,0:08:28.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们既然把机会漏失了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.98,0:08:31.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那还有什么希望可言呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.46,0:08:37.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也就是说我们这个星球，注定是要灭亡了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.60,0:08:39.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们懂了没有?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.60,0:08:40.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个星球啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.88,0:08:42.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要灭亡…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.50,0:08:45.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老大…那怎么办啊?我不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.66,0:08:48.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哭什么!我也很痛苦…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.48,0:08:50.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在胡说八道什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.26,0:08:53.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.20,0:08:55.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那还用说吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.56,0:08:59.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉克尔赫普的失败，那就表示这个星球要毁灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.96,0:09:01.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要乱讲!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.80,0:09:02.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是因为这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.88,0:09:05.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们到这把年纪还没什么成就
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.10,0:09:08.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们做什么都得要有自信才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.30,0:09:11.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们没有工作又身无分文
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:13.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找不到女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.24,0:09:14.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能独身
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.70,0:09:17.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那妳也不用这样说我们嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:22.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个为什么就不能学着什么事都向前看呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.26,0:09:23.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样会有用吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:25.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.82,0:09:28.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉克尔赫普，这一次的确是没有把敌人给打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.38,0:09:31.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我们还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.90,0:09:33.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们应该还能做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.38,0:09:39.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照时间看来…\N克劳德他们现在一定已经入侵到魔石索沙里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.50,0:09:42.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克劳德这次可是豁出性命来战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.64,0:09:46.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了保护这个星球，可是拼尽全力的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.60,0:09:47.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.30,0:09:48.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要相信希望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.80,0:09:50.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望…?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.24,0:09:53.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果放弃的话就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.08,0:09:56.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管那本古书上的预言是怎么写的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.08,0:09:58.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这场战斗还没有结束…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.60,0:10:05.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还没有输
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.00,0:10:10.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.40,0:10:11.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老大…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.50,0:10:13.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.00,0:10:16.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我们现在应该怎么办呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.74,0:10:18.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么…我们可以帮的上忙的地方吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.10,0:10:21.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我打算把那艘宇宙飞船修好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.00,0:10:22.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来帮忙吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.08,0:10:24.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我们几个帮得了忙吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.94,0:10:27.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然可以啰，我还是个机械白痴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.90,0:10:28.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.28,0:10:31.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们只要照我说的做就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.60,0:10:34.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至于困难的部分，就交给我们好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.78,0:10:35.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.84,0:10:38.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.82,0:10:41.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这句话真不错…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.80,0:10:44.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我过去从没有相信过什么事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.70,0:10:52.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得身体…好热…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.20,0:10:54.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会有这种感觉?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.38,0:10:58.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克劳德…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.60,0:10:59.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.88,0:11:01.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么都找不到路呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.50,0:11:03.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该有条路会通到上面去才对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.16,0:11:05.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路啊…?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.18,0:11:05.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.96,0:11:15.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空破斩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.60,0:11:20.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.30,0:11:31.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对，她不是我们的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.84,0:11:36.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.10,0:11:38.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点，来吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.04,0:11:40.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.08,0:11:42.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.50,0:11:46.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.20,0:11:53.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阶梯…?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.48,0:12:16.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火凤破
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.20,0:12:23.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能量光箭(EnergyArrow)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.50,0:12:28.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳还真有魄力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.10,0:12:29.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.74,0:12:32.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们都把我的皮肤弄成这个样子了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.28,0:12:35.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得这不算什么伤呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.70,0:12:37.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.74,0:12:39.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有，没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.00,0:12:44.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧，轮到你大显身手了 艾修顿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.98,0:12:49.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现在的工作就是\N尽可能把这些怪物拦在这个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.80,0:12:52.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.30,0:12:53.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.86,0:12:54.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小长，小圆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.40,0:13:00.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的对手是我们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.20,0:13:11.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣堂?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.14,0:13:14.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔石索沙里…怎么会有这种地方呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.42,0:13:20.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.80,0:13:23.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…怎么会这样?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.42,0:13:26.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.46,0:13:28.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.64,0:13:40.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜…终于见到妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.50,0:13:44.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在等着见妳的这一天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.70,0:13:49.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过没想到我们会在这样的情况下见面…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.34,0:13:51.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.20,0:13:55.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟妳是同一种人 尼德行星的子民啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.10,0:13:57.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尼德行星?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.80,0:14:01.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳胸前的那个坠子就是尼德子民的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.26,0:14:08.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也难怪妳会这么惊讶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.40,0:14:09.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟在这之前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.04,0:14:13.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳一直以为妳是这个艾斯贝尔星上的居民
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.50,0:14:16.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是妳确实是我们的同胞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.32,0:14:20.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔石索沙就掌控在我们的手中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.00,0:14:23.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掌控魔石索沙?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.62,0:14:24.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.00,0:14:26.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停止战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.70,0:14:29.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我们一起保护魔石索沙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.06,0:14:31.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胡说…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.30,0:14:33.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.42,0:14:34.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的同胞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.00,0:14:37.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.50,0:14:49.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜，等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.86,0:14:52.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.00,0:14:54.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.80,0:14:58.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.04,0:15:00.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.10,0:15:03.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们说的不是真的，对不对?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.40,0:15:05.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.28,0:15:07.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是他们的同族…对吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.40,0:15:10.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.00,0:15:13.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们掌控的魔石索沙…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.80,0:15:16.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要毁灭这个艾斯贝尔星的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.64,0:15:19.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然是我原来出生的星球上的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.60,0:15:21.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.60,0:15:22.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你走吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.10,0:15:26.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能再跟在你身边了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.66,0:15:27.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜 …
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.60,0:15:29.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这是真的话
