Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.00,0:16:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了能够保护这个星球拼命战斗着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.64,0:16:23.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.84,0:16:26.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是你的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.80,0:16:30.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.42,0:16:33.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.40,0:16:41.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克劳德…
