Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.04,0:17:43.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.60,0:17:50.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想帮他…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.20,0:17:53.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的…想助他一臂之力…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.30,0:17:56.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想保护我最重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.36,0:17:58.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克劳德…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.00,0:18:01.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在这个星球上遇见你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.80,0:18:03.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想失去这个星球
